$$FOP = {{Number\; of\; optimized\; codons} \over {Total\; number\; of\; codons}},$$\end{document}FOP=NumberofoptimizedcodonsTotalnumberofcodons,where the optimized codons were determined from the reference codon frequencies from the DNA for the corresponding taxon. Like CAI, values closer to 1 indicate a higher level of codon optimization. FOP and CAI values are generally well correlated (Bahiri-Elitzur & Tuller, 2021).

